OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA mix of sunny spells and some
OL,6,Fwell scattered showers. Cloud building
OL,7,Flater with some wet and windy weather
OL,8,Farriving during the evening.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,11,Fclearing Tuesday to a mix of sunshine
OL,12,Fand blustery showers. Further showers
OL,13,Fpossible on Wednesday, then turning
OL,14,Fdrier, brighter and warmer on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
